Get the collections implemented in the package

Source: R/mf_list_collections.R
mf_list_collections.Rd

Get the collections implemented in the package and a set of related information

mf_list_collections()

Value

A data.frame with the available collections, and a set of related information. Main columns are :

collection

Collections name

source

Data provider

long_name

Collection long name

doi

DOI of the collection

start_date

Start date for the collection

url_opendapserver

URL of the OPeNDAP server from which the data is extracted

Examples
